{"tid":2241621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文: 最近我的推特和IG上出現許多印度網友，我很高興能代表台灣和大家打招呼！","createTime":"2020-10-13T12:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T13:34:36.000Z","uid":51271,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f49deb331f2215d90374e16ddcdfedd50f78a97f","tid":2241621,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/posts/10157064698846065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftsaiingwen%2Fposts%2F10157064698846065&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=626bc37d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/posts/10157064698846065</a><br />\n<br />\n蔡英文 Tsai Ing-wen<br />\n <br />\ntSSponnso5rmend<br />\n  &middot;<br />\n最近我的推特和IG上出現許多印度網友，我很高興能代表台灣和大家打招呼！<br />\n#Namaste🙏to our friends from #India 🇮🇳! Thank you for following me here. Your warm regards remind me of fond memories from time spent in your incredible country, your architectural marvels, vibrant culture &amp; kind people are truly unforgettable. I miss my time there dearly. <br />\nNamaste（這是印度梵文的問候語）！來自印度的朋友們，大家好！謝謝大家關注我。 你們溫暖的問候，勾起我在印度這個不可思議的國家所留下的美好回憶。 你們令人驚艷的建築、生機蓬勃的文化和親切善良的人民，都讓我難以忘懷。 我真心想念我在印度的時光。<br />\n➡️來我的Twitter看更多：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/iingwen/status/1315966767567495170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiingwen%2Fstatus%2F1315966767567495170&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=645db8c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiingwen%2Fstatus%2F1315966767567495170&h=cc6cbb6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/iingwen/status/1315966767567495170</a>"},{"pid":"656f8af37ca1c4679108ae4689b95af5012a4ea3","tid":2241621,"uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:11:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/iingwen/status/1315966767567495170\" data-sr-url=\